Term 42 Editor

2x4 Octant character editor for the terminal, in color

Dependencies:
python 3
blessed

Keys:

Shift+Q - quit
Left Arrow, a - move left
Right Arrow, d - move right
Up Arrow, w - move up
Down Arrow, s - move down
Space - toggle pixel
r - resize canvas
g - toggle zoomed view grid
z - toggle zoomed view color
Shift+X - clear canvas
Home, h - home position (0, 0)
e - find nearest edge when off canvas
Shift+M - change color mode (16, 256, DIRECT), clears canvas
c - select foreground color
Shift+C - select background color
p - put color in 2x4 cell
Shift+P - pick color from 2x4 cell
Shift+S - save file

In palette selection screen:
Arrows - move around
Enter - select
Escape - cancel

In DIRECT mode selection screen:
q - red +1
w - green +1
e - blue +1
a - red -1
s - green -1
d - blue -1
Shift+Q - red +10
Shift+W - green +10
Shift+E - blue +10
Shift+A - red -10
Shift+S - green -10
Shift+D - blue -10
Enter - select
Escape - cancel

At any text prompt:
Escape - cancel operation
Enter - submit answer

Known Bugs/Issues:
The status/prompt lines don't clear.
No backspace in prompts.
